name: Auckland Drift Collective
description: Premier drift club in Auckland focusing on skill development, safety, and building the drift community. Weekly practice sessions and monthly competitions.

name: Euro Owners NZ
description: Exclusive club for European car enthusiasts. BMW, Audi, Mercedes, VW, and more. Focus on quality builds and technical discussions.

name: JDM Legends
description: Celebrating Japanese automotive heritage. From classics to modern JDM. Monthly meets, technical workshops, and track days.

name: Stance Culture NZ
description: Low and slow lifestyle. Bags or static, we appreciate the art of stance. Photo meets, shows, and building the stance community.

name: Track Day Warriors
description: Serious about track performance. Safety-focused club for track day enthusiasts. Coaching, timing, and competitive events.

name: Rotary Club NZ
description: For those who worship the Dorito engine. RX-7, RX-8, and rotary swaps welcome. Technical support and parts sharing.
